{
  "id": "adv_main_03_07_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章32話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃をおとしめる発言は許しませんわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t allow you to speak ill of Kotono!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 4.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに琴乃は悩んでいました。ずっと、ずっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that Kotono kept thought about it all the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "けれどそれは、月ストのセンターという重い責任を\n背負い、常に私達のことを考えていたからですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s because she was carrying the heavy responsibility\nof being Moon Tempest’s center and was always thinking about us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 21.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "脱退するのが無責任？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Withdrawing is irresponsible?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が軽い気持ちでそんな行動を起こさないことは\n私達がこの世界で一番、誰よりも知っていますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We know better than anyone in the world‚ more than anyone else‚\nthat Kotono wouldn’t take such an action lightly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.199998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.5666660309
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 36.799998347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が……あの子が一体どれほど悩んでいたのか\n考えただけで苦しくて、辛くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just thinking about how much Kotono…\nhow much she was struggling is painful and agonizing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.799998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.399998347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "何よりも、同じグループの仲間でありながら\n手を差し伸べられなかったことが悔しくて……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than anything‚ I regret that I couldn’t reach out to her\neven though we were in the same group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.099998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.5999968211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、琴乃はいつだって真摯に、月ストと……\nアイドルというものに向き合ってきたのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ Kotono has always been sincere and dedicated to\nMoon Tempest… and to being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7666634877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、琴乃を悪く言うのはやめてくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please stop badmouthing Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1999940236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.2666606903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、すずちゃんと同じ気持ちです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We feel the same way as Suzu-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666606903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 68.6333288829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな琴乃ちゃんを尊敬してて……今でも大好きです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We all respect Kotono and… we still love her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6333288829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.1666622162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、琴乃ちゃんの意志を尊重した上で……\n私達は、四人でも活動を続けることを決めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why‚ while respecting Kotono’s will…\nwe’ve decided to continue our activities as four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3999980927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.4666611989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "な、なるほど……分かりました。質問は以上です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I understand. I have no more questions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4666611989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "私達のこれからを……どうか見守ってくださいませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you please… watch over our future?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5333278656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.5333278656
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 94.6999945323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……そろそろお時間ですので、他にご質問が\nないようであれば、記者会見はこの辺りで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We’re running out of time‚ so if there are no more questions‚\nwe’ll end the press conference here――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4540568592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最後に、よろしいでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "May I ask one last question?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.4978454828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.6311788161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は以前より月の……いえ、月ストのファンでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been a fan of Moon… no‚ Moon Tempest‚ for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6311788161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからこそ、長瀬さんの脱退はとても残念に思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I’m very disappointed about Nagase-san’s withdrawal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4666637421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 113.5645050287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでも……四人で続けていくことを決めた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still… I respect and support your decision",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5645050287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みなさんの覚悟を、心から尊重し、応援します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to continue as four from the bottom of my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3999945323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.9999970754
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 121.3978342931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いばらの道を歩まれるみなさんの、決意の言葉を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you all‚ who are about to embark on a thorny path‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3978342931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "改めて一言、お聞かせ願えますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "share a few words of your determination…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7718096067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.9978342931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "素敵なお言葉、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your kind words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9978342931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 132.1978342931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん。改めて……本当に申し訳ありません\n今まで五人の月ストを応援していただいたファンの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone. Once again… we’re truly sorry.\nTo the fans who've supported the five of Moon Tempest up until now‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1978342931,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3466.666666700007,
          "startTime": 138.6333278656
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.0645233393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "こうして温かい言葉をかけてくださるみなさんには\nこれからの活動で誠意を見せたいと思っています",
      "translations": {
